STRING: Looking up at the sky, lost in thought.

LABEL: 0xDAF1
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xDAFF
STRING: "I wonder if there used to be someone here. Or if... there was no one here all along."

LABEL: 0xDB88
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xDB96
STRING: "What if I've come here too late? What should I do then?"

LABEL: 0xDC09
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xDC17
STRING: "What if someone you were supposed to meet left you behind, and you didn't know..."

LABEL: 0xDCAC
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xDCBA
STRING: "Maybe, that also happened to me when I was still alive."

LABEL: 0xDD3B
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xDD49
STRING: "If everything was already over by the time I was born till now...... what is the value of my existence?

LABEL: 0xDDE3
STRING: A kitten with clear green eyes appeared beside her.

LABEL: 0xDE46
STRING: The kitten rubbed against her and curled up, snuggling up next to her.

LABEL: 0xDEBF
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xDECD
STRING: "What are you doing here, holed up in a place like this, all alone...?"

LABEL: 0xDF54
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xDF62
STRING: "It's no use, I couldn't change... I couldn't change anything..."

LABEL: 0xDFE3
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE031
STRING: Before she knew it, the kitten was licking the reddened part of her arm.

LABEL: 0xE0B0
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE0BE
STRING: "As I thought, you saw it too? But I don't feel any pain, so I'm fine. He said it too, that it looked painful..."

LABEL: 0xE169
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE177
STRING: "It was the first time someone other than Papa cared about me..."

LABEL: 0xE1F2
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE200
STRING: "I won't say anything about Papa... No, the less he knows the happier he'll be."

LABEL: 0xE291
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE29F
STRING: "I honestly don't know anymore, maybe I've started looking for a reason, like for whose sake these wounds are for... who am I doing this for?"

LABEL: 0xE360
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE36E
STRING: "In the end, maybe this is just the embodiment of a scream that can't be put into words, and I just wanted someone to worry about me."

LABEL: 0xE403
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE411
STRING: "...Am I really making the right choice by staying here?"

LABEL: 0xE486
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE494
STRING: "I hated everything in the world, made excuses, and ran away instead of trying...... and I was ashamed of myself for that."

LABEL: 0xE533
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE541
STRING: "I want to exist not for myself... but for someone else. I want to be someone who can get over any painful experience for the sake of someone I care about."

LABEL: 0xE5F6
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE604
STRING: "Is it... arrogant of me to have such a big wish?"

LABEL: 0xE67F
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE68D
STRING: "I've been thinking a lot about it... and I'm sure there's no right answer."

LABEL: 0xE70E
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE71C
STRING: "It's hard being alone. It hurts. It's so painful to be alive... I'm sure that... you're suffering, too."

LABEL: 0xE7D5
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE7E3
STRING: "...I'll give you the release that you deserve."

LABEL: 0xE84C
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE85A
STRING: "This place is a terribly cold and... lonely place. No one can see you. No sunlight will reach you. Night lasts for eternity..."

LABEL: 0xE8FB
STRING: Girl

LABEL: 0xE909
STRING: "Goodbye, this world. I am... already... no longer here."

LABEL: 0xE96F
STRING: The girl began to walk away slowly.

LABEL: 0xE9B4
STRING: Leaving everything behind in this place.

LABEL: 0xEA09
STRING: And...

LABEL: 0xEA40
STRING: Now that the girl was no longer there... only one thing remained.

LABEL: 0xEA9F
STRING: The bloodied remains of the kitten were left lying on the ground.
